---
description: Testability
globs:
  - "**/*.py"  # Apply to all Python files
  - "**/*.pyi" # Apply to Python stub files
alwaysApply: true
---

Write code with testability in mind. Aim for pure functions where possible, minimize side effects, and structure code (e.g., using dependency injection) to make unit testing easier (e.g., allowing mocks/stubs).

